  "description_snippet": "# VULNERABILITY DETAILS\n\nRuntime function `Runtime_TypedArraySet` converts `HeapNumber` to `size_t` at [1] and [2]. When `offset + length` overflows, `CHECK` at [3] in function `CopyElementsHandleImpl` can be bypassed. So `destination->DataPtr() + offset * element_size` can be outside the address sp"
